iration/Refer: [a=Charles Mingus] on Candid/[a=Eric Dolphy]/[a=Paul Bley]•[a=Bob Demmon] + [a=The Astronauts (3)]•[a=Little Feat]•[a=Ruins]/[a=Booker T & The MG's]/Colin Wilson•[a=Ennio Morricone]/[a=Albert King]/[a=Chuck Brown]•[a=Orchestra Baobab]/[a=Takeshi Terauchi]/[a=El Hadj M'Hamed El Anka]•[a=The Accüsed]/[a=The Meters]/Yakuza Zankoku Hiroku•[a=The Tony Williams Lifetime]/[a=O.L.D.]•[a=Anthony Braxton]/[a=Anton Webern] \"Six Bagatelles\"/[a=Sammy Cahn] \"Guess I'll Hang My Tears Out to Dry\"/[a=Frank Sinatra]/[a=Morton Feldman]•[a=Carl Stalling]/[a=Igor Stravinsky]•[a=Melvins]/[a=The Beatmasters]/[a=Septic Death]/Hellfire/Leather Folk (the Book)•[a=Abe Schwartz]/[a=Ivo Papasov]/[a=Naftule Brandwein]•[a=Repulsion]•[a=Led Zeppelin]/[a=Edo Akemi] and [a=Jagatara]/[a=Bernard Herrmann]•[a=Santana]/[a=Extreme Noise Terror]/[a=Conway Twitty]•[a=Agnostic Front]/[a=Siege (2)]•[a=Ornette Coleman]/[a=Corrosion of Conformity]/[a=Massacre]/[a=Quincy Jones]•Sam Fuller/[a=Funkadelic]/[a=Carcass]•[a=Liberace]/[a=Jan Hammer]/[a=Napalm Death]/[a=Ed Blackwell]/[a=Charlie Haden]/[a=Mick Harris]/[a=Carole King]/[a=Red Garland]/[a=Boredoms]/[a=Jerry Reed]/[a=SPK]/Roger Williams.\n. Published by Theatre of Musical Optics, BMI.\n. Recorded April 1992. Mixed September 1992.\n\n• Absinthe:\n. Recorded at Electric Lady, NYC, December 1992.\n. Mixed at Platinum Island, NYC,  January 1993.\n. Published by Theatre of Musical Optics, BMI.\n\n• Leng Tch'e\n. Published by Theatre of Musical Optics, BMI.\n\nNaked City ℗  1989 Elektra Nonesuch\nGrand Guignol ℗ 1992 Avant\nHerectic ℗ 1992 Avant\nRadio ℗ 1993 Avant\nAbsinthe ℗ 1993 Avante\nLeng Tch'e ℗ 1992 Hips Road\nthis compilation © ℗ 2005 Tzadik\n\nTomoyo T.L. (Karath=Razar)\nLisa Wells (Strong Silent Type)","identifiers":[{"type":"Barcode","description":"Text","value":"7 02397-73442 0"},{"type":"Barcode","description":"String","value":"702397734420"},{"type":"Matrix / Runout","description":"CD1","value":"TZACD73441 1J 01 K"},{"type":"Matr